  </ThingDef>
  <!-- Dark Sapling -->
  <ThingDef ParentName="MOL_SaplingBase">
    <defName>MOL_Sapling_Dark</defName>
    <label>dark schrat sapling</label>
    <description>A small, twisted mass of dark branches and roots crudely shaped into a vaguely humanoid form. These entities can temporarily animate when disturbed by logging or fire, moving through shadowed undergrowth with jerky, unsettling movements. Psychoreactive alterations from ancient archotech presence enable the defensive behavior, though whether this was deliberate or accidental remains unknown. The animation eventually fades, leaving behind what appears to be ordinary dead wood. The mechanism and purpose are poorly understood.</description>
  </ThingDef>
  <PawnKindDef>
    <defName>MOL_SchratDark_Sapling</defName>
    <label>dark schrat sapling</label>
    <race>MOL_Sapling_Dark</race>
    <combatPower>30</combatPower>
    <lifeStages>
      <li>
        <bodyGraphicData>
          <texPath>Things/Pawn/Animal/MOL_SaplingDark/MOL_SaplingDark</texPath>
          <graphicClass>Graphic_Multi</graphicClass>
          <drawSize>3</drawSize>
        </bodyGraphicData>
      </li>
    </lifeStages>
    <aiAvoidCover>true</aiAvoidCover>
    <destroyGearOnDrop>true</destroyGearOnDrop>
  </PawnKindDef>
  <!-- Plains Sapling -->
  <ThingDef ParentName="MOL_SaplingBase">
    <defName>MOL_Sapling_Plains</defName>
    <label>plains schrat sapling</label>
    <description>A compact assemblage of pale wood and tangled roots roughly organized into a small humanoid shape. When threatened, psychoreactive alterations allow these formations to achieve mobility across open terrain. How such alterations spread to grassland flora across multiple worlds suggests global archotech activity, though the reason for animating simple vegetation is baffling. The entity returns to dormancy once the disturbance ceases, indistinguishable from dead brush. No satisfactory explanation exists for this phenomenon.</description>
  </ThingDef>
  <PawnKindDef>
    <defName>MOL_SchratPlains_Sapling</defName>
    <label>plains schrat sapling</label>
    <race>MOL_Sapling_Plains</race>
    <combatPower>30</combatPower>
    <lifeStages>
      <li>
        <bodyGraphicData>
          <texPath>Things/Pawn/Animal/MOL_SaplingPlains/MOL_SaplingPlains</texPath>
          <graphicClass>Graphic_Multi</graphicClass>
          <drawSize>3</drawSize>
        </bodyGraphicData>
      </li>
    </lifeStages>
    <aiAvoidCover>true</aiAvoidCover>
    <destroyGearOnDrop>true</destroyGearOnDrop>
  </PawnKindDef>
</Defs>
